reviews.text: Cute, trendy and quiet. Great location in Causeway Bay and perfect if you're looking for a place to really boost your social media feed. The pancakes are nice and fluffy, rainbow cake is quite dense and not very sweet - well balanced. Staff take good care of customers and are used to people coming in just for the perfect photo for IG ^^ Some of the bottled drinks are a gamble. The strawberry latte in this photo ended up quite sour, should stick to coffee next time
it looks like a dessert café from fairytale! in busan, korea the shop is huge and they are famous for their rainbow cake.
